## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
Is the identifier of your physical sample present in the metadata for the digital data that associates to it? Will you be able to locate the physical sample if you have the digital data? And how about the reverse?

~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
與您的數位資料相對應的後設資料中，是否包含該實體樣本的識別碼？如果您手上有數位資料，是否能夠據此找到對應的實體樣本？反過來也是如此嗎？

~~~
